{"title":"Prevelo Bikes Offers New Designs, Carbon Bits and Kid Friendly Grips","link":"https://bikerumor.com/prevelo-kid-bikes-updated-designs-carbon-components/","date":1683299894000,"content":"<p>Prevelo has become one of my favorite booths at the <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/prevelo-zulu-line-microshift-1x-for-small-wheels-heir-kid-specific-flat-pedals/\" target=\"_blank\">Sea Otter Classic</a>. They always have new components designed for kids, and their stoke for getting youth on bikes is contagious.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-crankset-carbon-close-up-.jpeg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"600\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-crankset-carbon-close-up--800x600.jpeg\" alt=\"Prevelo Bikes Updated designs at sea otter classic crankset carbon close up\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-crankset-carbon-close-up--800x600.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-crankset-carbon-close-up--297x223.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-crankset-carbon-close-up--120x90.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-crankset-carbon-close-up--768x576.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-crankset-carbon-close-up-.jpeg 1280w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>For 2023 the kid-centric brand rolled new models and some larger (26″ wheeled) bikes. They also showcased updated components and carbon accessories, available soon to bling out your kiddos’ ride.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Prevelo Bikes — Updated Designs</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-new-colors-.jpeg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"600\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-new-colors--800x600.jpeg\" alt=\"Prevelo Bikes Updated designs at sea otter classic new colors\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-new-colors--800x600.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-new-colors--297x223.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-new-colors--120x90.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-new-colors--768x576.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-new-colors-.jpeg 1280w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Several updated frame designs were at the Prevelo booth for Sea Otter Classic. The one that stuck out the most to me was the updated Alpha. The Alpha is the all-arounder bike from Prevelo. It’s capable of dirt, road, gravel, and so on.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Prevelo Alpha Two</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-Alpha-two-.jpeg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"600\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-Alpha-two--800x600.jpeg\" alt=\"Prevelo Bikes Updated designs at sea otter classic Alpha two\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-Alpha-two--800x600.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-Alpha-two--297x223.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-Alpha-two--120x90.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-Alpha-two--768x576.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-Alpha-two-.jpeg 1280w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The Alpha Two received a very cool seatpost update, making it much easier for small riders. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-new-seatpost-.jpeg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"600\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-new-seatpost--800x600.jpeg\" alt=\"Prevelo Bikes Updated designs at sea otter classic new seatpost\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-new-seatpost--800x600.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-new-seatpost--297x223.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-new-seatpost--120x90.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-new-seatpost--768x576.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-new-seatpost-.jpeg 1280w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-seapost-upclose-.jpeg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"600\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-seapost-upclose--800x600.jpeg\" alt=\"Prevelo Bikes Updated designs at sea otter classic seapost upclose\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-seapost-upclose--800x600.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-seapost-upclose--297x223.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-seapost-upclose--120x90.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-seapost-upclose--768x576.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-seapost-upclose-.jpeg 1280w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-.jpeg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"600\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic--800x600.jpeg\" alt=\"Prevelo Bikes Updated designs at sea otter classic\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic--800x600.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic--297x223.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic--120x90.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic--768x576.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-.jpeg 1280w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The design is similar to a BMX seat and post combo but maximizes the amount of the post that can enter the frame. Prevelo had to redesign their seatpost clamps to get the proper clearance. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-seatpost-hole.jpeg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"600\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-seatpost-hole-800x600.jpeg\" alt=\"Prevelo Bikes Updated designs at sea otter classic seatpost hole\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-seatpost-hole-800x600.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-seatpost-hole-297x223.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-seatpost-hole-120x90.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-seatpost-hole-768x576.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-seatpost-hole.jpeg 1280w\" /></a><figcaption>Super easy chain guard removal </figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-details-.jpeg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"600\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-details--800x600.jpeg\" alt=\"Prevelo Bikes Updated designs at sea otter classic details\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-details--800x600.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-details--297x223.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-details--120x90.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-details--768x576.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-details-.jpeg 1280w\" /></a><figcaption>Extended seat tube with an open bottom to allow excess seatpost to travel. </figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-easy-to-remove-chain-guard-.jpeg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"600\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-easy-to-remove-chain-guard--800x600.jpeg\" alt=\"Prevelo Bikes Updated designs at sea otter classic easy to remove chain guard\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-easy-to-remove-chain-guard--800x600.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-easy-to-remove-chain-guard--297x223.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-easy-to-remove-chain-guard--120x90.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-easy-to-remove-chain-guard--768x576.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-easy-to-remove-chain-guard-.jpeg 1280w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The result is a slammed seatpost that allows a child to grow into the bike and get the most use of the frame.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Prevelo Alpha Three – Four – Five</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-Alpha-series-.jpeg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"763\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-Alpha-series--800x763.jpeg\" alt=\"Prevelo Bikes Updated designs at sea otter classic Alpha series\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-Alpha-series--800x763.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-Alpha-series--297x283.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-Alpha-series--120x114.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-Alpha-series--768x732.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-Alpha-series-.jpeg 1280w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>As for the Alpha Three, Four, and Five, the frame is notably different, with an extra bit of tire clearance and compliance in the rear. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-alpha-.jpeg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"600\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-alpha--800x600.jpeg\" alt=\"Prevelo Bikes Updated designs at sea otter classic alpha\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-alpha--800x600.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-alpha--297x223.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-alpha--120x90.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-alpha--768x576.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-alpha-.jpeg 1280w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Pervelo designs the frames so it’s easier for kids to get on/off the bikes and feel confident while pedaling. This new frame design and some very new electric colorways look to accomplish that.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Larger Tires — Prevelo Zulu Five</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-26.jpeg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"600\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-26-800x600.jpeg\" alt=\"Prevelo Bikes Updated designs at sea otter classic 26\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Previously the Prevelo sizing maxed out at a 24″ wheeled bike. Now they are moving into 26″ land, and the bikes are getting more serious. The new Prevelo Zulu Five is the newest addition to the brand lineup. It is the first 26″ mountain bike they have offered. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-zulu.jpeg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"600\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-zulu-800x600.jpeg\" alt=\"Prevelo Bikes Updated designs at sea otter classic zulu\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-zulu-800x600.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-zulu-297x223.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-zulu-120x90.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-zulu-768x576.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-zulu.jpeg 1280w\" /></a><figcaption>Pervelo Zulu 24″ gets a new electric blue paint job for 2023 and beyond.</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The bike is very close in appearance to its brethren in Zulu, but the addition of 26″ wheels opens up more possibilities for tires, forks, and rims. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-tires-.jpeg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"600\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-tires--800x600.jpeg\" alt=\"Prevelo Bikes Updated designs at sea otter classic tires\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-tires--800x600.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-tires--297x223.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-tires--120x90.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-tires--768x576.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-tires-.jpeg 1280w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The Zulu Five (and others) roll on WTB tubeless STi rims, Kenda Regolith Pro 2.40″ tires, and more to offer.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Hier Components — Carbon Upgrades </h2>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-carbon-kids-crank.jpeg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"461\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-carbon-kids-crank-800x461.jpeg\" alt=\"Prevelo Bikes Updated designs at sea otter classic carbon kids crank\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-carbon-kids-crank-800x461.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-carbon-kids-crank-297x171.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-carbon-kids-crank-120x69.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-carbon-kids-crank-768x442.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-carbon-kids-crank.jpeg 1280w\" /></a><figcaption>The new Heir carbon crankset features a direct mount chain ring and narrow stance width. </figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Prevelo has an in-house component line, Heir. They offer aftermarket kid-fit cranksets, handlebars pedals, and other accessories. Previously the components were only offered alloy and different anodized color offerings.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-crankset-carbon-close-up-.jpeg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"600\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-crankset-carbon-close-up--800x600.jpeg\" alt=\"Prevelo Bikes Updated designs at sea otter classic crankset carbon close up\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-crankset-carbon-close-up--800x600.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-crankset-carbon-close-up--297x223.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-crankset-carbon-close-up--120x90.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-crankset-carbon-close-up--768x576.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-crankset-carbon-close-up-.jpeg 1280w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-carbon-crankset-details-.jpeg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"600\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-carbon-crankset-details--800x600.jpeg\" alt=\"Prevelo Bikes Updated designs at sea otter classic carbon crankset details\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-carbon-crankset-details--800x600.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-carbon-crankset-details--297x223.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-carbon-crankset-details--120x90.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-carbon-crankset-details--768x576.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-carbon-crankset-details-.jpeg 1280w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>For 2023 Prevelo is stepping it up and offering a carbon crankset (145mm) that works in many frames. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-clamp-zone-.jpeg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"600\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-clamp-zone--800x600.jpeg\" alt=\"Prevelo Bikes Updated designs at sea otter classic clamp zone\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-clamp-zone--800x600.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-clamp-zone--297x223.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-clamp-zone--120x90.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-clamp-zone--768x576.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-clamp-zone-.jpeg 1280w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-carbon-bars-.jpeg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"591\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-carbon-bars--800x591.jpeg\" alt=\"Prevelo Bikes Updated designs at sea otter classic carbon bars\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-carbon-bars--800x591.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-carbon-bars--297x220.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-carbon-bars--120x89.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-carbon-bars--768x568.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-carbon-bars-.jpeg 1280w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-19mm-bars-.jpeg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"600\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-19mm-bars--800x600.jpeg\" alt=\"Prevelo Bikes Updated designs at sea otter classic 19mm bars\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-19mm-bars--800x600.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-19mm-bars--297x223.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-19mm-bars--120x90.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-19mm-bars--768x576.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-19mm-bars-.jpeg 1280w\" /></a><figcaption>19mm diameter bars to work with its new Heir 19mm lock on grips. </figcaption></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>They are also venturing into the handlebar category, releasing a carbon bar with 19mm grips, feature designers found needing to be improved in the cockpit world. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-19mm-grips-.jpeg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"600\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-19mm-grips--800x600.jpeg\" alt=\"Prevelo Bikes Updated designs at sea otter classic 19mm grips\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-19mm-grips--800x600.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-19mm-grips--297x223.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-19mm-grips--120x90.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-19mm-grips--768x576.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-19mm-grips-.jpeg 1280w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>In addition to the carbon bars, Hier will offer aftermarket 19mm lock-on grips, perfect for young riders.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Updated Spec</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-new-TekTro.jpeg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"554\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-new-TekTro-800x554.jpeg\" alt=\"Prevelo Bikes Updated designs at sea otter classic new TekTro\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-new-TekTro-800x554.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-new-TekTro-297x206.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-new-TekTro-120x83.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-new-TekTro-768x532.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Prevelo-Bikes-Updated-designs-at-sea-otter-classic-new-TekTro.jpeg 1280w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>As for updated specs, Prevelo is moving away from the Radius line of brake sets and starting to spec TekTro brake systems on their bikes. The Prevelo team liked the robust design of the TekTro and the limited need to service.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><em>For more information on Prevelo bikes, check out: <a href=\"https://prevelo.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Prevelo.com</a></em></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/prevelo-kid-bikes-updated-designs-carbon-components/\">Prevelo Bikes Offers New Designs, Carbon Bits and Kid Friendly Grips</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Jordan Villella","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"9c2db12c17dc350c1218824b479aad1df1b281fd463132a842a842b6f0e890aa","category":"Cycling"}